MARKET HEALTH OVERVIEW
% if ($variant eq 'dominated') {
<strong><%= $top_faction %></strong> dominated the exchange floor with <strong><%= $influence %></strong> influence (<%= $competing %> factions active). Competing buyer agents were consistently outbid.
Assessment: BUYER'S MARKET — influence concentrated under single entity.
% } else {
No single faction seized control this season — <strong><%= $competing %></strong> groups circled one another, each holding ground but none breaking through.
Assessment: FRAGMENTED DEMAND — multiple buyers competing creates favorable conditions for price negotiation.
% }
